  "important_notes": [
    "All Config classes use @attrs.define(slots=False) + @make_freezable decorator — instances are immutable after freeze()",
    "CallBackGroup..__getattr__ provides transparent fan-out: any method call dispatches to all registered Callback instances",
    "NVTXCallback pushes/pops NVTX ranges around forward/backward/optimizer/dataloading phases for profiling",
    "EMAModelTracker stores EMA weights as nn.Module buffers (dot→dash name mapping); PowerEMATracker uses iteration-dependent beta via EDM2 polynomial",
    "FastEmaModelUpdater is stateless (no buffers) – designed for FSDP where buffer-based EMA breaks",
    "ema_scope() context manager temporarily swaps model weights to EMA for validation then restores",
    "ImaginaireTrainer.training_step handles gradient accumulation via grad_accum_iter counter",
    "TrainerConfig.callbacks defaults: EMAModelCallback + ProgressBarCallback (LazyDict instantiation via hydra-style _target_)",
    "WeightTrainingStat is abstract (ABC + abstractmethod forward); tracks video/image samples, iterations, hours as persistent buffers",
    "TrainingStats is a plain @dataclass (not a nn.Module) — value object returned by WeightTrainingStat.get_training_stats()"
  ]
